  "off.lockedUnit": {"en":"🔒 Unit size & pricing on upgrade","fr":"🔒 Surface et tarifs après mise à niveau","de":"🔒 Flächengröße & Preise nach Upgrade","es":"🔒 Superficie y precios al mejorar el plan","it":"🔒 Superficie e prezzi con upgrade","nl":"🔒 Oppervlakte & prijzen na upgrade"},
